rComments: Good lecture; Passionate about his work; Really supportive on group project

Martineau is really passionate about what he does and it makes you want to go to his class, especially if you're really into finance. Great lecturer, knows how to get his point across, and very supportive with assignments outside of class.

Quite handsome, ok at teaching. Easier concepts he can explain well, but harder ones you sometimes feel like he doesn't even get it himself (although he does, but he has to think, and cannot explain clearly.) Lenient grader, kinda tell you what kinds of questions will be tested.
